						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/March-2012-K4D-Newsletter" title="March 2012 K4D Newsletter" alt="document">March 2012 K4D Newsletter</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>Download below the March 2012 K4D newsletter.</p>
							<p><span class="date">8/05/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="document" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/March-2012-K4D-Newsletter">Read more...</a>
</div>
