<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/IRETA-SPAN-March-2012-newsletter" title="IRETA SPAN March 2012 newsletter" alt="document">IRETA SPAN March 2012 newsletter</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>The Institute for Research, Extension and Training in Agriculture (IRETA), University of the South Pacific, has released the South Pacific Agricultural News (SPAN) electronic bulletin for March 2012. In this SPAN issue, you will read about the USP-EU Global Climate Change Alliance project in Samoa, the 16th international Symposium of the Society for Tropical Root Crops, the Samoa USP Alafua Agriculture Scholarships, among other interesting news clippings from the region.(IRETA, 03/2012)</p>
